<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="nl">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Top 2000 - Home</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #22282e 60%, white 40%);
            color: white;
        }

        .contact-box {
            background-color: white;
            color: black;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: background-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

            .contact-box:hover {
                background-color: #f8d7da;
                transform: translateY(-10px);
            }

        .contact-btn {
            background-color: #D32F2F;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

            .contact-btn:hover {
                background-color: #d43f3f;
            }

        .contact-box img {
            width: 120px;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 2px solid #D32F2F;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding-left: 0;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

            ul li {
                margin: 10px 0;
            }

        .container {
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        .row {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

            .row .col-md-4 {
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

            .header h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
                font-weight: bold;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .header p {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="header">
        <h1>Neem Contact Op</h1>
        <p>We staan klaar om je te helpen! Kies het beste contactmiddel voor jou.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="contact-box">
                    <img src="/image/Phone.png" alt="Telefoon">
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Tel.Nr. Studio:</strong> 0800-1122 (gratis)</li>
                        <li><strong>Adres:</strong> Postbus 26444, 1217 ZL Hilversum</li>
                        <li><strong>Bezoekadres:</strong> Bart de Graaffweg 2</li>
                    </ul>
                    <a href="tel:+318001122" class="contact-btn">Bel ons</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="contact-box">
                    <img src="/image/Berichten.png" alt="Berichten">
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>E-mail:</strong> info@radio2.nl</li>
                        <li><strong>Adres:</strong> Postbus 26444, 1217 ZL Hilversum</li>
                        <li><strong>Bezoekadres:</strong> Bart de Graaffweg 2</li>
                    </ul>
                    <a href="mailto:info@radio2.nl" class="contact-btn">Stuur een E-mail</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
